{"id":589021,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/【麻辣总局】不惜一切代价？你就是那个代价/","date":"2018-07-13T08:36:28Z","modified":"2018-07-14T16:55:44Z","title":"【麻辣总局】“不惜一切代价？你就是那个‘代价’！”","content":"<p>中美贸易摩擦再次升级，商务部霸气声明“<strong>不惜付出任何代价</strong>坚决回击”。中国网民如是说——</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0217.jpg\"><br />\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-589022 size-medium\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0217-300x221.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"221\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0217-300x221.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0217-768x566.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0217-1024x754.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>（【转】晚上吃饭时，一个半生不熟的朋友跟我说，美国太不是东西了，跟我们打贸易战。“我们不惜一切代价，也要打赢贸易战”。我心想，你也不照镜子看看自己，你是那个‘我们’吗？其实你就是那个“代价”。）</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>商务微新闻 |<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%E5%95%86%E5%8A%A1%E5%BE%AE%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%EF%BD%9C%E5%95%86%E5%8A%A1%E9%83%A8%E5%8F%91%E8%A1%A8%E5%A3%B0%E6%98%8E/\"> 商务部发布声明</a></li>\n<li class=\"title\">【真理部】<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/06/%E3%80%90%E7%9C%9F%E7%90%86%E9%83%A8%E3%80%91%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B4%B8%E6%98%93%E6%88%98%E7%AD%89/\">关于中美贸易战等</a></li>\n<li class=\"title\">美国之音 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%B9%8B%E9%9F%B3-%E8%B4%B8%E6%98%93%E6%88%98%E6%B0%91%E7%B2%B9%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E9%A4%90%E5%8E%85%E7%BB%99%E7%BE%8E%E6%B8%B8%E5%AE%A2/\">贸易战民粹化 一中国餐厅给美游客“加税”</a></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n","author":1056,"categories":[18270,18269,17016,10466,13789],"tags":[23753,32327]}